overview: Artisan Exhibits is a full-service trade show exhibit company founded by experienced trade show marketers to establish a new standard for quality and customer service in the events industry. At Artisan Exhibits, we’re focused on listening to your needs and developing a comprehensive and creative solution that is a perfect for your event schedule. We are a proud distributor of Nomadic Display products, known for their superior quality and unmatched warranty. Whether you need a tabletop booth in Las Vegas, or an island exhibit in Barcelona, we’ve got you covered with a wide selection of scalable exhibits and accessories, award-winning design and a dedicated exhibit expert to guide you through every step of the process. Give us a call and we’ll help you maximize your marketing budget and minimize the time needed to manage it all.
